Maintainer: Chris Hanretty <chris.hanretty@rhul.ac.uk>
Description: The \code{sharesimulatoR} package offers functions for simulating realistic party systems of a given size and for plotting the simulated seat/vote shares of the top-ranking parties. It also features an interactive Shiny GUI for these tasks.
